<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="closely-adv">closely <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kləʊsli/    美 /'kloʊsli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>接近地；仔细地；严密地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The students were sitting closely together and whispering. 
学生们紧挨着坐在一起窃窃私语。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Watch</strong> the pets <strong>closely</strong> when they are left outdoors.
把宠物放在室外时要仔细照看他们。</p><footer>2012 全国改</footer></div></div>